5BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&h=b0428a21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%89%88%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E7%A6%81%E6%92%AD%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1/</a><br />\n另外有少少野想講:<br />\n<br />\n我想你地知道呢啲微小既事係唔應該WFC<br />\n我自己認為香港人行到今時今日<br />\n唔係因為反送中<br />\n唔係因為假普選<br />\n而係因為我地知道支共係垃圾,係地球毒瘤<br />\n呢件事由8964,甚至可能係國共內戰時期已經開始被世人知道<br />\n當中可能就係一件一件微小既事累積而黎<br />\n我唔知呢0.01%對將來會有幾大影響<br />\n但係我相信今日就係每個0.01夾埋得出黎既結果<br />\n<br />\n同埋我想講 現實唔同打機 所有事都唔會有take2<br />\n輸咗係唔會有得restart<br />\n所以!!!<br />\n珍惜當下每一個機會 累積些微既勝機<br />\n最後先會贏到呢個Raid Boss<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"856d3df70c43529599e1cfa623fac0699a960e11","tid":1953354,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"遲下禁止香港人講廣東話架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6766313ba4f3f683ce138e2c2136467ef06f19","tid":1953354,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"禁返佢個APP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b984f2489794b239887d681499634bb301e2498","tid":1953354,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"進攻功能界別 不如 進攻抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抖音廣東話過半 = 有話語權（機會大過玩功能界別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"8a78506421223587941205ff57f5897ecc8b77e2","tid":1953354,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"好多外國人用架<br />\n推"},{"pid":"4df0c0087224e1cff